Factorial and Fish

A salty recipe for a fine fish. A tad raw, but definitely salty.

Ingredients.
1 salmon
1 pinch salt

Methods.
Take salmon from refrigerator.
Put salt into mixing bowl.
Carve the salmon.
Combine salmon.
Put salmon into mixing bowl.
Remove salt.
Fold salmon into mixing bowl.
Continue until carved.
Pour contents of the mixing bowl into the baking dish.

Serves 1.